<p><b>Amy Hempel</b> (born <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1951-12-14"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="12-14"><a href="/wiki/December_14" title="December 14">December 14</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1951" title="1951">1951</a></span>) is an <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">American</a> <a href="/wiki/Short_story" title="Short story">short story</a> writer, <a href="/wiki/Journalist" title="Journalist">journalist</a>, and university <a href="/wiki/Professor" title="Professor">professor</a> at <a href="/wiki/Brooklyn_College" title="Brooklyn College">Brooklyn College</a>.</p>
